WEBVTT

00:01.600 --> 00:02.976
I want to know how the best
bawd in London

00:03.000 --> 00:04.320
snags a virgin.

00:04.400 --> 00:07.240
Secure me a pretty maid
and be sure to test her

00:07.320 --> 00:08.720
about her virtue.

00:08.800 --> 00:10.640
I want you to go to Justice Hunt

00:10.720 --> 00:12.320
and to tell him that
Margaret Wells

00:12.400 --> 00:15.800
is forcing girls
to work against their will.

00:15.880 --> 00:17.760
I can't marry him.
You will marry him!

00:17.800 --> 00:19.960
There's a little Quiggy
growing inside me.

00:20.000 --> 00:21.480
I'm a Spartan too.

00:21.520 --> 00:24.520
You've killed. With one stab.

00:24.640 --> 00:26.000
Charlotte sent me.

00:26.120 --> 00:27.640
And what does Charlotte
want us to do?

00:27.760 --> 00:30.120
We need to buy a virgin.

00:30.160 --> 00:32.200
What are you doing?
This man is a liar

00:32.280 --> 00:33.640
and a thief, put him out.

00:33.680 --> 00:34.960
Get off me.

00:35.000 --> 00:36.880
Unsullied virgin
or deceitful whore.

00:36.960 --> 00:38.720
On this occasion, you lose.

00:38.840 --> 00:40.400
Lydia.

00:40.520 --> 00:42.040
Lydia, let me out!

